    <note>Ren(1) Zhuan [874] He moved his lineage (zu) from Qingzhou, Shouguang xian to Caozhou, Dingtao xian. His kinsmen had moved their lineage members (zuren) with them to the location of their official posts at least twice before. His son-in-law, Zeng(1) Xiaozhang [3905], was Zeng(1) Gongliang's [8136] nephew. Zhuan's grandson Zhiqi's [3427] family moved to Dongping, Xucheng xian. XCB, 130.1a, 163.5b, 165.8a, 166.17a; Liu(2) Qi, WJ, 8.97-8; Luo Chenyu, Manglo zhongmu yiwen sibian, 6.39b-47a; SS, 330.1a. CBD, 1, 654-5.</note>
